INUMBER 999
NAME 308
WEIGHT 10
VOLUME 2
WORN_WRIST
*DESCRIPTION_START
The torc is a spiral of golden yellow metal worked with silvery patterns
that draw your gaze in a circle. You feel magic at work as your eyes follow
the path traced by the ancient ghoulish artisian.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LOOK -1
	IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER Yo! If your INTNUM3 is not equal to 1, this thing casts UNSTUN on you. So don't look at it when you're hidden, dude. Oh, and this is meant to be unique. Oh, yeah, it has to be worn to work.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
		IFITEM -1 WORN
      IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! TIM
        ECHO ALL %A radiates a burst of reddish flames!
        SPELL 338
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 TIM
      ENDIF
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GAZE -1
	IFITEM -1 WORN
    CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER You feel your eyes grow warm and the world seems to turn bright red for a moment as fire flashes in your eyes.
		ECHO OTHERS Fire flashes in %n's eyes, casting a scarlet glow across the area.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TURN -1
	IFITEM -1 WORN
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER As you turn your arm within the torc your clenched fist bursts into flame!
		ECHO OTHERS Scarlet flames rise from %n's clenched fist!
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
	IFITEM -1 WORN
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER You adjust the torc to fit you more comfortably.
		ECHO OTHERS %N adjusts %a to a more comfortable position on %h arm.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WAVE -1
	IFITEM -1 WORN
		CLEARVERB
		ECHO PLAYER Flames rise from your hands and arc between them, filling the air with the scent of brimstone!
		ECHO OTHERS %N raises both hands and flames leap between them, filling the air with the scent of brimstone!
	ENDIF
ENDIF

