;
; fragment for chameleons
INUMBER 1118
NAME 981
SKIN
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE INSUBSTANTIAL
REAGENT
IFPREVERB GET -1
IFVAR ITEMVAL1 ! 2000
RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 10
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER As your hand touches a silver fragment, it pulses with life!
DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 20 You reel in pain as your life force is drained.
ECHO OTHERS %n touches a silver fragment and screams in horror!
ECHO ALL The air glitters and sparkles.
RANDOM DUMMY1 1 2 0
IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
GENMON 213
ELSE
GENMON 215
ENDIF
REMOVEITEM -1
ELSE
EQUAL ITEMVAL1 2000
ECHO PLAYER A silver fragment shudders as you pick it up.
ECHO OTHERS A silver fragment shudders as %n picks it up.
ECHO PLAYER You feel the fragment absorb some of your life force.
ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RUB -1
CLEARVERB
IFVAR INTNUM59 > 0
ECHO PLAYER Your body returns to normal phase.
EQUAL INTNUM59 0
ECHO OTHERS %N rubs a silver fragment and shimmers for a moment.
ECHO ALL A silver fragment vibrates and crumbles to dust.
REMOVEITEM -1
ELSE
ECHO PLAYER A silver fragment crumbles to dust as you rub it.
ECHO OTHERS A silver fragment crumbles to dust as %n rubs it.
SPELL 342
REMOVEITEM -1
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RECALL -1
IFVAR INTNUM59 = 0
IFVAR SKILL32 > 1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER As you study the fragment, the phase of your body changes.
ECHO OTHERS %N studies a fragment and shifts out of focus for a moment.
EQUAL INTNUM59 1
ECHO ALL A silver fragment crumbles to dust.
REMOVEITEM -1
ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER You draw upon the energy stored the fragment.
IFVAR INTNUM59 = 0
EQUAL INTNUM59 10
ECHO PLAYER Horrible pain wracks your body as you open a phase vortex.
ECHO OTHERS %n gazes at a fragment and a phase vortex rips the air.
ECHO ALL A silver fragment grows dim and crumbles to dust.
REMOVEITEM -1
PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
ECHO PLAYER You feel your phase shifting as you fade in and out of reality.
  ECHO OTHERS %n fades in and out of reality.
DAMAGEPLR SLASH 40 Light crystallizes around %n.
   PLREVENT 2
   CONTPLREVENT
ECHO PLAYER You feel your phase shifting as you fade in and out of reality.
  ECHO OTHERS %n fades in and out of reality.
DAMAGEPLR SLASH 50 Light crystallizes around %n.
   PLREVENT 3
   CONTPLREVENT
ECHO PLAYER You feel your phase shifting as you fade in and out of reality.
  ECHO OTHERS %n fades in and out of reality.
DAMAGEPLR SLASH 60 Light crystallizes %n.
ECHO ALL The phase vortex subsides.
ELSE
RANDOM DUMMY3 1 20 0
IFVAR SKILL32 > DUMMY3
ECHO PLAYER The life force in the fragment restores you.
SPELL 338
SPELL 318
ECHO ALL A silver fragment grows dim and crumbles to dust.
REMOVEITEM -1
ELSE
ECHO PLAYER You cannot quite attune yourself to the fragment.
SPELL 318
ECHO ALL A silver fragment grows dim and crumbles to dust.
REMOVEITEM -1
ENDIF
ENDIF

ENDIF

