INUMBER 364
  NAME 96
  MISC
  WEIGHT 1
  VOLUME 3
  ARTICLE A
  CONTAINER UNDER
  INTERIOR 20
  SUBSTANCE BRITTLE
  WORN_DON
  IFPREVERB2 PUT -1
    IFVAR ARCHNUM ! 364
      CLEARVERB
      IFVAR ARCHNUM > 98
        IFVAR ARCHNUM < 158
          ECHO PLAYER You carefully scrutinize %a through your monocle.
          ECHO OTHERS %N carefully scrutinizes %a through %h monocle.
          STRCVT 0 ITEMVAL1
          ECHO PLAYER You estimate its worth at about %0 copper coins.
          ECHO PLAYER [Round: 5 secs]
          EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
        ELSE
          ECHO PLAYER Your monocle can only appraise gems and jewelry.
        ENDIF
      ELSE
        ECHO PLAYER Your monocle can only appraise gems and jewelry.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
